Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE ORICHALCUM WARRIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, the Hero was lost in the waters\Nnear the Field of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was wounded by Lord Hadorra,\Nno one believes he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive out there somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mystic Legion must be the first\Nto find Dai and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We must distinguish ourselves\Nfor Dark King Ban's praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go! Mystic Legion, go forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me and my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Find something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, there won't be any smell\Nto detect in this environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, Meruru, could have been\Na real help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She has that strange power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't bring her here.\NShe's just a defenseless Seer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find a single clue\Nlooking from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looks like it's\Nwinter swimming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Shouldn't you warm up first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. I thought that\Nthis was my chance to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation is very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare a simple jellyfish laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I've got a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it worth your while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is hopeless!\NI can barely last a few minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's down there,\Nnot even Dai could survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he's not here in the water,\Nsearching is going to be near impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Another possibility is that\Nwhen he hit an iceberg,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he got buried inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we find him\Nfrom among all these icebergs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How can you be fishing\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This may look like fishing to a layman,\Nbut it has a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind works on\Na whole different level from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A jellyfish I just tamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having it search for Dai\Nin return for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. A Fat Rat is like\Nthe king of the monster world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Any monster will bow before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dai's! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really search everywhere?!\NWasn't there a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves that he's definitely nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the food I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. I haven't caught it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai... Don't die. Don't die out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many hundreds\Nor thousands of icebergs there are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard Popp's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the others be nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last bit of Aura I have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that pillar of light be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is pathetic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was all right, that rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Your voice must have reached him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Big Guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy has also noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a search team\Nsent by Zaboera to find Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Melt the iceberg and rescue Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay alone, Big Guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a little soon\Nfor you to worry about me, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then! I'll leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitors have no business here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You always hide in the shadows\Nand never get your hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet here you are with your servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you've lost standing\Nwithin the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hide behind others,\Nleeching off their efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and never work to better yourself,\Nyou're bound to end up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly where you are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll take care of\Nboth you and Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the time apart\Nhas made you forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the Beast King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying Flayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of the crest is fading!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry! They need me out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ULTRA COMBUSTION SLASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera has discovered Dai\Nand headed out to the frozen sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool has gotten ahead of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym, use force if necessary.\NBring Zaboera back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No one shall touch\NDai and his friends but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be careful from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you standing around for!\NLeave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Rattus Rocket Ram!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dai!\N-Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Dai, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously. Who else\Nwould come to rescue you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And me! And me!\NDon't forget about me, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu, carry that sword!\NWe're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But what about my praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can a sword so small weigh so much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! How did he get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying Flayers! Cast Merazoma on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my greatest trump card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the convergence spell, Mahoplus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Super Spell that\Nlets me absorb others' spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,add my own power\Nand fire the combined energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,With the combined Merazoma spells\Nfrom me and my Flying Flayers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll evaporate you and that iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I run with a Rura spell,\Nit'll hit Chiu behind me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I cancel it out\Nwith a spell of my own?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! W-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A man made of metal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a new enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did it save them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Zaboera doesn't recognize him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Lord Hadorra's loyal soldier,\Nthe pawn, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he say pawn?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By Lord Hadorra's order I've come\Nto retrieve your disobedient hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! My spell didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nyou already repelled my Mahoplus spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of the ultimate guards created\Nfrom an Orichalcum piece by Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My entire body is made of Orichalcum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am invulnerable to\Nall attacks and spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Lord Hadorra with his Orichalcum blade\Nor the omnipotent Dark King can harm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of that sword\Nmight actually put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not kill us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother protecting us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a piece of scum like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a proud servant of Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will face any opponent head-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing you in such a cheap way\Nwould be boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I protect the Field of Death with\Nmy four comrades by Lord Hadorra's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall cross paths eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better train\Nfor when that day comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappoint Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we were rescued by our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy, that guy said he was a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By pawn, did he mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's the name\Nof the weakest chess piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the weakest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scary thought, but it seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot to do\Nwhen we get back to Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot\Nyou're wounded and half-frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Back to Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can figure things out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about your landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me! I'm overburdened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have seen me out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Dai! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the power\Nto escape that cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cool your head there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you steal my glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to see Hadorra's\Nnewly assembled royal guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving him five whole Orichalcum warriors\Nwas rather generous of you, King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mere Gargoyles and Archdemons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be strong enough\Nto be Hadorra's guard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great Dark King Ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I present to you my new servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Five pieces born from\Neverlasting Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the pawn, Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,PAWN: HYM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The knight, Sigma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,KNIGHT: SIGMA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The bishop, Fenbren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,BISHOP: FENBREN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The rook, Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,ROOK: BLOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the queen, Albinass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,QUEEN: ALBINASS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate force\Nto protect the Field of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the Hadorra Royal Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the king of that royal guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Disciples of Aban are defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world is conquered,\NI shall grant you the surface world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you may reclaim your title of Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The showdown\Nwith Dark King Ban is decided.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Disciples of Aban\Nbegin their individual training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To fight the Hadorra Royal Guard,\Nwho are immune to magic,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp visits his mentor, Matorif.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to learn the ultimate spell\Nthat even Matorif fears to use,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp begins a deadly training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Extreme Annihilation Spell, Medroa"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
